<i>adverb</i>: 추근추근 [추근추근], 찐득찐득 [찐득찐득], 진득이 [진드기], 바득바득 [바득빠득] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>추근추근 [추근추근]</dt><br>
<dd>tenaciously; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 태도가 끈질긴 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a tenacious nature or attitude.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>찐득찐득 [찐득찐득]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stickily; glutinously</dd><br>
<dd>눅눅하고 끈기가 있어 끈적끈적하게 자꾸 달라붙는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being damp and sticky enough to adhere to something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. toughly</dd><br>
<dd>질겨서 잘 끊어지지 않는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being tough enough not to fall apart.</dd><br>
<dd>3. patiently; tenaciously</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 행동이 매우 질기고 끈기가 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one’s personality or behavior being very patient and persistent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진득이 [진드기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. patiently; tenaciously</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 행동이 몹시 질기고 끈기가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of one’s personality or behavior being very patient and persistent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. stickily; glutinously</dd><br>
<dd>잘 끊어지지 않을 정도로 눅눅하고 끈기가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being damp and sticky enough not to fall apart.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>바득바득 [바득빠득]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stubbornly; obstinately</dd><br>
<dd>억지를 쓰며 자꾸 우기거나 조르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of persisting or importuning unreasonably over and over.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tenaciously</dd><br>
<dd>악착스럽게 애쓰는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of making great effort.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>